                    <WebAddress>https://www.esrl.noaa.gov/gmd/ccgg/ghgpower</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header/>
                <Paragraph>"The Power of Greenhouse Gases" web page presents examples of the excess heat that the Earth system is retaining. The amount of excess heat is sufficiently large to force climate change on a regional and global scale.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
